The quality-adjusted life-years in the oncological patients' health-related 
quality of life.

Kucnerowicz K(#)(1), Pietrzak A(#)(2)(3), Cholewiński W(4), Martenka P(5), 
Marszałek A(6), Burchardt E(4), Strzesak E(4).

Author information:
